		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CIV5_BUILDINGS_RIAD_TEXT">
			<Text>A riad is a traditional Moroccan house with an interior garden or courtyard. The word riad comes from the Arabian term for garden, "ryad". The riads were inward focused, which allowed for family privacy and protection from the weather in Morocco. </Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_RIAD_STRATEGY">
